    public abstract class AmpAutocompleteFieldPanel<CHOICE>
extends AmpFieldPanel<CHOICE>
implements org.apache.wicket.ajax.IAjaxIndicatorAware
    Autocomplete Combobox Component based on YUI 2.8.x (or upper). This component can be used to show an autocomplete editbox http://developer.yahoo.com/yui/examples/autocomplete/ac_combobox.html
    Since:
    Jun 14, 2011
    See Also:
    http://ptrthomas.wordpress.com/2009/08/12/wicket-tutorial-yui-autocomplete-using-json-and-ajax/}, Serialized Form
